---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Support" description="Support, FAQ, and contact information for Departure: Fitness Quest">
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Support</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-12">We're here to help. Most questions are answered below — if not, reach out directly.</p>

      <!-- Contact card -->
      <div class="bg-surface/50 border border-surface-light/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
          Email us anytime and we'll get back to you within 1–2 business days.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:departure@engagequalia.com"
          class="inline-block text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors font-medium"
        >
          departure@engagequalia.com
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-text-muted text-[15px] leading-relaxed">

        <!-- Account & Sign-in -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Account &amp; Sign-in</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">I can't sign in to my account</h3>
              <p>
                Double-check your email and password, and try tapping "Forgot Password" on the sign-in screen to reset it.
                If you still can't get in, email us with the email address on your account and we'll help recover it.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I change my email or password?</h3>
              <p>
                Open the app → <strong class="text-text">Profile</strong> tab → <strong class="text-text">Settings</strong> → <strong class="text-text">Edit Profile</strong>.
                You can update your display name and avatar there. For email or password changes, email us and we'll assist.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I delete my account?</h3>
              <p>
                Open the app → <strong class="text-text">Profile</strong> → <strong class="text-text">Settings</strong> → <strong class="text-text">Delete Account</strong>.
                This permanently removes your profile, workouts, photos, purchase records, and all other data. You can also email us at
                <a href="mailto:departure@engagequalia.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">departure@engagequalia.com</a>
                to request deletion. Full details are in our
                <a href="/privacy#account-deletion" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Workouts & Scoring -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Workouts &amp; Scoring</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">My workout didn't earn XP</h3>
              <p>
                Departure has anti-cheat rules to keep leaderboards fair. If a workout exceeds category weight limits, posts
                more than 3 workouts in one day, or shows a sudden volume spike, XP may be reduced or blocked. You'll see an
                alert explaining why. The full scoring rules are available in the app under <strong class="text-text">Profile → How Scoring Works</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do Personal Records (PRs) work?</h3>
              <p>
                The app auto-detects PRs using the Epley 1-rep-max formula for strength lifts, longest duration for cardio,
                and fastest time for races. Beating a PR awards bonus XP and can unlock equipment. View your full PR history
                in the <strong class="text-text">Trophy Case</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Why is my rank not going up?</h3>
              <p>
                Ranks advance based on total XP earned across all workouts. There are 24 individual rank tiers (8 titles × 3
                sublevels each). If your XP is increasing but rank isn't, you may be between sublevels — check the
                <strong class="text-text">Ranks</strong> page in-app for the thresholds.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Purchases -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Purchases &amp; Subscriptions</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">I bought something but didn't receive it</h3>
              <p>
                Tap <strong class="text-text">Restore Purchases</strong> at the bottom of the Premium Store. The app re-checks
                Apple's records and re-delivers any unfulfilled purchase automatically. If the item still doesn't appear
                after 60 seconds, email us with your Apple receipt and we'll resolve it manually.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I restore purchases on a new device?</h3>
              <p>
                Sign in with the same account and tap <strong class="text-text">Restore Purchases</strong> in the Premium Store.
                All non-consumable items (equipment slots, banner packs, treasure trails, permanent XP multipliers) will be
                restored automatically.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I request a refund?</h3>
              <p>
                Refunds for App Store purchases are handled directly by Apple. Go to
                <a href="https://reportaproblem.apple.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">reportaproblem.apple.com</a>,
                sign in with your Apple ID, and request a refund for the purchase. If you need help explaining the issue to
                Apple, email us and we'll provide context.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Are in-app purchases required to play?</h3>
              <p>
                No. Departure is fully playable for free — all core features including workout tracking, rank progression,
                PRs, teams, journey battles, and AI future-self generation are free. In-app purchases are cosmetic or
                convenience upgrades (extra equipment slots, XP boosts, premium banners).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Future Self / AI -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Future Self &amp; AI Images</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">My future-self image didn't generate</h3>
              <p>
                AI image generation occasionally fails due to network issues or temporary service outages. Pull down on the
                Future Self screen to retry. If it fails three times in a row, restart the app. Each account includes a
                monthly allotment of free generations — buying additional image credits is optional.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Can I delete an AI-generated image?</h3>
              <p>
                Yes. Go to <strong class="text-text">Profile → Future Self</strong>, tap the image, and select "Delete." The
                image is permanently removed from our servers within 24 hours.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Will my selfie be used to train AI models?</h3>
              <p>
                No. Selfies are used only to generate your personal future-self images and are not used for model training,
                shared with third parties for marketing, or retained beyond what's needed to show you your transformation.
                See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
                for full details.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Teams & Battles -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Teams &amp; Battles</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I join a team?</h3>
              <p>
                In the <strong class="text-text">Arena</strong> tab, tap <strong class="text-text">Discover Teams</strong> to
                browse public teams, or enter an invite code from a friend. You can be a member of one team at a time.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Why can't I fight the next monster?</h3>
              <p>
                Teams advance through the journey map linearly — you must defeat each monster in order. After a battle
                (win or lose), there's a 24-hour cooldown before the next fight. The cooldown timer is shown on the
                monster's info screen.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I leave a team?</h3>
              <p>
                Open your team's page → <strong class="text-text">Settings</strong> → <strong class="text-text">Leave Team</strong>.
                Team owners must transfer ownership or disband the team before leaving.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Technical &amp; Bugs</h2>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">The app is crashing or freezing</h3>
              <p>
                Force-quit the app and reopen it. If the issue persists, restart your device. If it still crashes,
                email us with a description of what you were doing when it happened — screenshots or a screen recording
                help a lot.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">Notifications aren't showing up</h3>
              <p>
                Check iOS Settings → Notifications → Departure and confirm notifications are allowed. Within the app,
                go to <strong class="text-text">Profile → Settings → Notifications</strong> to verify workout reminders
                are enabled.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text mb-2">My data isn't syncing across devices</h3>
              <p>
                Data syncs through your account, so make sure you're signed in with the same email on both devices.
                Pull down to refresh on the Home screen to force a sync. If data still isn't appearing, email us with
                your account email and we'll investigate.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Legal links -->
        <div class="border-t border-surface-light/50 pt-8 mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Legal</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li>
              <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">
                Terms of Use (Apple Standard EULA)
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Still need help -->
        <div class="border-t border-surface-light/50 pt-8 mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Still need help?</h2>
          <p>
            Email us at
            <a href="mailto:departure@engagequalia.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-light transition-colors">
              departure@engagequalia.com
            </a>
            and include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-2 mt-3">
            <li>The email address on your Departure account</li>
            <li>Your device model and iOS version</li>
            <li>A description of the issue, ideally with a screenshot or screen recording</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            We typically respond within 1–2 business days.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
